di Bandung.

311
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,720
Ternyata begitu.

312
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:07,200
Terima kasih sudah menjaga Aa Eros.

313
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:11,560
Bibi merasa amat sedih
saat tahu Aa Eros koma.

314
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:16,040
Padahal Aa Eros sangat sayang
kepada Bibi.

315
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:22,720
Kak Eros pasti akan sembuh, Bi.

316
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:23,920
Pasti.

317
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:28,080
Aku yakin Eros
pasti sembuh sebentar lagi.

318
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:31,120
Amin.

319
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:35,440
Baik. Dimakan dulu kudapannya, ya?
Sekalian diminum juga.

320
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:38,040
- Bibi ke dapur dulu.
- Terima kasih, Bi.

321
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:48,120
Aiden.

322
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,240
Apa?

323
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,400
Wajahmu terlihat sangat parah.

324
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:54,640
Mau diobati dulu?

325
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:00,640
- Kau sangat manis.
- Aku serius.

326
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,560
Sangat manis.

327
00:29:02,600 --> 00:29:06,560
Apa? Aku membutuhkan perhatian
dari Serra, bukan kau.

328
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:08,760
- Aku pergi dulu.
- Mau ke mana?

329
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:12,520
Wajahku terluka.

330
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:14,400
Hatiku lesu, butuh diisi ulang.

331
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:15,680
Mengerti?

332
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:21,240
Melihat Serra saja
sudah membuatku merasa senang.

333
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:25,800
Aku pergi. Tos dulu.

334
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:33,640
- Aku pergi dulu.
- Hati-hati.

335
00:29:57,800 --> 00:30:00,000
Astaga.

336
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:02,040
Masih silau?

337
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:04,000
Sudah. Aku merasa malu dilihat orang.

338
00:30:04,040 --> 00:30:06,200
Biarkanlah.

339
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:09,880
Agar kau tidak kepanasan.
Belajar sajalah.

340
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:12,960
- Agar pintar.
- Bagaimana kalau kau lelah?

341
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:15,520
Tidak lelah.

342
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:23,320
- Terimalah!
- Terimalah!

343
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,360
Aku menyayangimu.

344
00:30:36,120 --> 00:30:37,560
Aku juga menyayangimu.

345
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,840
Selamat malam, Serra.

